<ContentLayout title="Climbing at the Ith" description="Climbing at the Ith: spectacular rock formations and marked routes in the Weserbergland." heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522163182402-834f871fd851?w=1920&h=800&fit=crop" heroImageAlt="Climber on a rock face" heroSubtitle="One of Northern Germany's most popular climbing areas">
  <h2>Climbing at the Ith</h2>
  <p>The <strong>Ith</strong> with its numerous rock formations is one of the best-known and most popular <strong>climbing areas in Northern Germany</strong>. The bizarre limestone cliffs along the ridge offer routes for beginners to advanced climbers.</p>

  <div class="bg-ith-red/10 border-l-4 border-ith-red rounded-r-xl p-6 my-8 not-prose">
    <h3 class="text-ith-red font-bold text-lg mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-anthracite">Climbing at the Ith is <strong>only permitted on marked and approved cliffs</strong>. Please respect nature reserves. Check current closures at <a href="https://ig-klettern-niedersachsen.de/klettergebiete/ith/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ith-blue underline">IG Klettern Niedersachsen</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Climbing Areas</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Adam und Eva</strong> – Classic routes for beginners</li>
    <li><strong>Rattenfängerplatz</strong> – Versatile wall with historical background</li>
    <li><strong>Teufels Küche</strong> – Challenging routes for experienced climbers</li>
    <li><strong>Ith Ridge Path</strong> – Combination of hiking and climbing</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Practical Information</h3>
  <div class="bg-sand rounded-xl p-6 my-8 not-prose">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Difficulty</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">UIAA III to IX – suitable for beginners and advanced climbers.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Equipment</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Own climbing equipment required. No rental available on site.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Best Season</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Spring to autumn. Rocks may be icy in winter.</p></div>
      <div><h4 class="font-semibold text-anthracite mb-2">Parking</h4><p class="text-anthracite-light">Trailhead car parks at the Ith ridge serve as starting points.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
